Dale Ishimoto https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dale_Ishimoto 0 Dale Ishimoto (April 3, 1923 – March 4, 2004) was an American actor of Japanese descent. He was born in Delta, Colorado in 1923 and was raised in Guadalupe, California. Dale_Ishimoto ( April_3_,_1923 – March_4_,_2004 ) was an_American_actor of Japanese_descent .
